headline: Seven Financial Institutions Leveraging Jack Henry Technology Win 2025 WebAwards
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc.® (Nasdaq: JKHY) is proud to announce that seven financial institutions have received WebAwards for websites built using Jack Henry web hosting and design services.

headline: 2 Safe-and-Steady Stocks to Consider Right Now and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: A stock with low volatility can be reassuring, but it doesn’t always mean strong long-term performance. Investors who prioritize stability may miss out on higher-reward opportunities elsewhere.
